            <div id="dsq-comment-message-11173" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Because bitcoins are digital, you can back up your wallet!  You can&#8217;t do that with paper money.  Hence if you lose your wallet, you go to the cloud and download your backed up encrypted wallet and off you go again. Advantage bitcoin.</p>
</div>
