http://profiles.google.com/justindkeith                <span id="dsq-author-user-9780">Justin Keith</span>
            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-9780" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-9780" class="dsq-comment-message"><p><a href="http://geraldcelente-blog.blogspot.com/2011/11/what-actually-happened-with-mf-global.html" rel="nofollow">http://geraldcelente-blog.blogspot.com/2011/11/what-actually-happened-with-mf-global.html</a></p>
