            <div id="dsq-comment-message-9784" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>It&#8217;s important to realize that bitcoins are not a form of money, they are merely a media of transaction.  See Carl Menger &#8220;On the Origins of Money&#8221; <a href="http://www.cooperativeindividualism.org/menger_money.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.cooperativeindividualism.org/menger_money.html</a></p>
</div>
